Oh Ha Na!

2
00:00:10,340 --> 00:00:12,100
Yes?

3
00:00:15,450 --> 00:00:19,940
You keep it.  It saved me many times during my trips.

4
00:00:29,600 --> 00:00:33,150
Episode 11

5
00:00:45,610 --> 00:00:47,950
Oh Ha Na

6
00:01:00,150 --> 00:01:01,240
Oh...

7
00:01:01,240 --> 00:01:03,300
It's been a long time.

8
00:01:18,400 --> 00:01:20,720
He's here. He's here.

9
00:01:20,720 --> 00:01:22,820
Who came?

10
00:01:22,820 --> 00:01:26,430
That Noona Ha Na's rabbit jerk.

11
00:01:33,850 --> 00:01:35,660
The sound is pretty awesome.

12
00:01:40,380 --> 00:01:43,550
Wow! Cha Seo Hoo is at our house. Come quickly!

13
00:01:43,550 --> 00:01:46,730
Won, I'm going home first.

14
00:01:47,540 --> 00:01:49,120
Okay.

15
00:01:57,340 --> 00:01:59,350
I'm sorry for the late greeting.

16
00:01:59,350 --> 00:02:03,550
Don't try to greet us. Leave.

17
00:02:03,550 --> 00:02:05,970
Wait, Honey...

18
00:02:05,970 --> 00:02:09,420
It's that... you coming here all of a sudden,

19
00:02:09,420 --> 00:02:11,810
what is it that you're trying to do?

20
00:02:11,810 --> 00:02:16,760
I'm sorry. I came to see Ha Na, but thought that I should pay my respects.

21
00:02:16,760 --> 00:02:20,110
What right do you have to see my daughter again?

22
00:02:21,630 --> 00:02:24,540
I'm sorry, but this time I won't disappoint again.

23
00:02:24,540 --> 00:02:27,150
Then, what is it that you want?

24
00:02:27,150 --> 00:02:30,840
- Why are you looking for her?
- What are you up to?

25
00:02:30,840 --> 00:02:34,740
I will marry Ha Na.

26
00:02:38,280 --> 00:02:39,940
Wow.

27
00:02:42,910 --> 00:02:45,490
Seo Hoo...

28
00:02:45,490 --> 00:02:47,060
Ha Na.

29
00:02:54,120 --> 00:02:55,590
Ha Na!

30
00:03:04,930 --> 00:03:07,680
Seo Hoo, you shouldn't do this.

31
00:03:07,680 --> 00:03:10,860
Did I do something wrong?

32
00:03:10,860 --> 00:03:15,140
It's not something you did wrong. But for marriage,

33
00:03:15,140 --> 00:03:17,990
you should have told me first.

34
00:03:17,990 --> 00:03:22,510
I've started to just barely calm my parents.

35
00:03:22,510 --> 00:03:24,980
This is a big deal.

36
00:03:24,980 --> 00:03:28,140
Don't you know how much we hurt my parents?

37
00:03:28,140 --> 00:03:30,280
I didn't come here thinking about that.

38
00:03:30,280 --> 00:03:32,720
I came just to see you, but since I met your brother,

39
00:03:32,720 --> 00:03:36,420
I thought I have to pay my respects to them, so I went in.

40
00:03:36,420 --> 00:03:40,590
They asked what my plans are, so I just answered.

41
00:03:40,590 --> 00:03:42,590
Because I will marry you for sure.

42
00:03:42,590 --> 00:03:45,550
The problem is not whether we get married or not.

43
00:03:45,550 --> 00:03:49,640
Can't you just think about my position?

44
00:03:53,980 --> 00:03:57,650
Dragging me away  in front of your parents,

45
00:03:57,650 --> 00:03:59,400
is that your position?

46
00:04:00,280 --> 00:04:02,990
- Seo Hoo.
- I'm trying. I'm doing my best.

47
00:04:02,990 --> 00:04:08,670
I think I'm going to be very angry, if I don't get some acknowledgment for the effort I'm extending.

48
00:04:16,440 --> 00:04:18,910
Today I am leaving first.

49
00:04:42,390 --> 00:04:45,520
Hyung, what are you going to do?  Cha Seo Hoo appeared suddenly at the house.

50
00:04:45,520 --> 00:04:47,920
Noona dragged him out.

