Should I call him Sir Rabbit?

86
00:08:14,590 --> 00:08:16,720
Or Rabbit-Sama?

87
00:08:26,270 --> 00:08:28,570
But, getting back together with that rabbit jerk is really not right.

88
00:08:28,570 --> 00:08:31,750
I won't ever ever again make it difficult for you because of my problem.

89
00:08:31,750 --> 00:08:34,740
What can be done when that's not possible.

90
00:08:34,740 --> 00:08:37,000
I'm trying my best.

91
