128
00:11:07,080 --> 00:11:11,130
I know you are trying. Thank you.

129
00:11:15,730 --> 00:11:18,700
The interior pressure of a bottle of champagne is six atmospheres.

130
00:11:18,700 --> 00:11:23,360
It is possible to be hit in the eye by the cork, so being cautions is most important.

131
00:11:23,360 --> 00:11:27,470
You take the foil off completely.

132
00:11:27,470 --> 00:11:30,140
Then press the top using your thumb.

133
00:11:30,140 --> 00:11:35,210
Hold the bottle lightly and pull up the pin then turn it six times.

134
00:11:35,210 --> 00:11:43,880
Start unraveling. One, two, three, four, five, six.

135
00:11:43,880 --> 00:11:47,230
After turning the sixth time, it is completely loosened.

136
00:11:47,230 --> 00:11:51,160
Pressure six and six times! Isn't it fun?

137
00:11:51,160 --> 00:11:56,040
It is important not to make noise opening a sparkling wine.

138
00:11:56,040 --> 00:11:59,880
If you turn it? Tada...

139
00:11:59,880 --> 00:12:02,280
It's easy, right?

140
00:12:02,280 --> 00:12:03,950
You give it a try. Oh ho!

141
00:12:07,330 --> 00:12:09,880
The top must not fly off like that.

142
00:12:18,980 --> 00:12:24,060
I think you have a talent for lecturing. Their level of focus is different.

143
00:12:24,060 --> 00:12:27,470
You became more charismatic after your trip.

144
00:12:27,470 --> 00:12:29,340
I always had charisma.

145
00:12:29,340 --> 00:12:35,990
No. Something is vaguely different. Like a manly charm or some...

146
00:12:35,990 --> 00:12:39,430
Madam Choi! Why are you doing this?

147
00:12:39,430 --> 00:12:43,240
Hey. In that manner, I am expecting you to join the meal vehicle event, okay?

148
00:12:43,240 --> 00:12:44,810
What is this...

149
00:12:44,810 --> 00:12:48,150
I am busy attending events after my picture got on the company publication.

150
00:12:48,150 --> 00:12:53,760
I am trying very hard to replace your lost opportunity on the training you gave up.

151
00:12:53,760 --> 00:12:57,790
Would you please give up that attempt, Madam Choi?

152
00:12:57,790 --> 00:13:00,570
This is Noona's heart watching you.

153
00:13:06,590 --> 00:13:08,610
So when is she arriving?

154
00:13:08,610 --> 00:13:11,030
I heard she is arriving on Wednesday.

155
00:13:11,030 --> 00:13:13,760
Then I should just play hard for a few days,

156
00:13:13,760 --> 00:13:16,650
because it will get really busy once the president arrives.

157
00:13:16,650 --> 00:13:21,880
I don't think she will sue you for a breach of contract, but I am worried.

158
00:13:21,880 --> 00:13:26,620
I am worried too because I can't play with a certain person once I get busy.

159
00:13:27,930 --> 00:13:30,260
But really... How could you do that ...

160
00:13:31,730 --> 00:13:34,630
Only look at Ha Na? (Hana means one)

161
00:13:34,630 --> 00:13:38,960
Since I've lost her once, I shouldn't this time.

162
00:13:38,960 --> 00:13:45,130
Right. The one whom you should never lose is really important of course.

163
00:13:47,660 --> 00:13:50,860
Do you just want to go back to America first?

164
00:14:01,330 --> 00:14:03,050
I got it. Got it!

165
00:14:03,050 --> 00:14:05,720
I really did have a lot of work to do today, Mom.

166
00:14:05,720 --> 00:14:08,530
I think your father will say something again.

167
00:14:08,530 --> 00:14:10,620
I am on my way home.

168
00:14:10,620 --> 00:14:13,570
Is that right? Then buy some night snacks on your way in.

169
00:14:13,570 --> 00:14:16,220
What is this? You just told me to hurry.

170
00:14:16,220 --> 00:14:17,460
I am a bit hungry.

171
00:14:17,460 --> 00:14:19,680
I got it.

172
00:14:22,590 --> 00:14:28,090
I'm really envious. I should have thought about doing that sooner.

173
00:14:31,430 --> 00:14:33,430
Welcome!

174
00:14:35,230 --> 00:14:36,020
What brought you here?

175
00:14:36,020 --> 00:14:38,550
Ah, mom wants some night snacks.

176
00:14:38,550 --> 00:14:41,900
- You should find another route!
- Look who's talking.

177
00:14:44,030 --> 00:14:46,430
You are alone at this time.

178
00:14:46,430 --> 00:14:50,070
Ah, I had too much work to do.

179
00:14:50,870 --> 00:14:53,290
You guys had a fight, didn't you.

180
00:14:53,290 --> 00:14:55,380
It's not like that.

181
00:15:08,930 --> 00:15:13,060
Is Unni Mi Hyang doing well? I haven't seen her a while.

182
00:15:13,060 --> 00:15:16,790
I think she is a bit busy these days. She became a fan of somebody else.

183
00:15:16,790 --> 00:15:21,520
Again? She has an overflowing energy.

184
00:15:21,520 --> 00:15:23,200
What about you?

185
00:15:24,980 --> 00:15:29,080
You are not too shabby when it comes to energy.

186
00:15:33,930 --> 00:15:36,020
You've been doing well, right?

187
00:15:40,830 --> 00:15:46,220
Now we are asking about each other an hour after we meet?

188
00:15:47,110 --> 00:15:50,060
I didn't ask if you were doing well.

189
00:15:52,070 --> 00:15:55,190
Of course I am doing well.

190
00:15:55,190 --> 00:15:57,380
Right.

191
00:15:57,380 --> 00:16:02,290
My work is going well and I am getting along with Cha Seo Hoo as well.

192
00:16:05,750 --> 00:16:09,130
Are you bragging that your relationship is going well now?

193
00:16:11,930 --> 00:16:15,380
Isn't that what you wanted to ask?

194
00:16:15,380 --> 00:16:18,060
That I am doing alright.

195
00:16:18,060 --> 00:16:21,130
You want to ask if Cha Seo Hoo is giving me a hard time.

196
00:16:28,260 --> 00:16:33,670
I am alright and everything's going well.

197
00:16:34,630 --> 00:16:37,130
I am telling you that.

198
00:16:55,520 --> 00:16:58,780
Your night snack is here!

199
00:17:00,080 --> 00:17:01,880
Yay!

200
00:17:02,540 --> 00:17:05,130
Try to get back home early.

201
00:17:05,130 --> 00:17:09,360
Mom, is that something you should say to a 34-year-old daughter?

202
00:17:09,360 --> 00:17:13,300
Is that something you should say in this situation?

203
00:17:13,300 --> 00:17:15,080
Sorry.

204
00:17:15,080 --> 00:17:18,660
You have a lot of things to be sorry about these days.

205
00:17:22,530 --> 00:17:26,440
Then what can I do? I like him.

206
00:17:26,440 --> 00:17:33,130
Aigoo... Because of the man who can only visit you a few times a year,

207
00:17:33,130 --> 00:17:38,470
and thinking about how you were making a ruckus rearranging your schedule to fit his...

208
00:17:38,470 --> 00:17:42,720
Aigoo, I still don't know about this.

209
00:17:42,720 --> 00:17:46,820
But why aren't you saying it can never be?

210
00:17:46,820 --> 00:17:51,550
If I say it could never be, then will you never see him again?

211
00:17:53,030 --> 00:18:00,200
I know one thing well about you. That is being stubborn which you took after me.

212
00:18:00,200 --> 00:18:06,690
If you'd give up because I am against it, then you wouldn't even have started it.

213
00:18:08,820 --> 00:18:10,750
Mom.

214
00:18:11,970 --> 00:18:18,820
But Oh Ha Na, falling on the same place twice,

215
00:18:18,820 --> 00:18:22,300
is pretty pathetic.

216
00:18:22,300 --> 00:18:24,030
Yeah.

217
00:18:25,570 --> 00:18:28,520
- How is Father?
- I don't know.

218
00:18:28,520 --> 00:18:34,010
He just takes it out on me!

219
00:18:36,410 --> 00:18:41,340
Aria Airline Meal Vehicle of Love

220
00:18:51,410 --> 00:18:54,290
Is your girlfriend not answering your call?

221
00:18:54,290 --> 00:18:56,490
I think it's over.

222
00:18:57,730 --> 00:19:00,440
Cheer up Sunbae.

223
00:19:00,440 --> 00:19:03,900
So you couldn't remember what that special date was?

224
00:19:03,900 --> 00:19:05,090
Yeah.

225
00:19:05,090 --> 00:19:08,250
Aigoo, aigoo.

226
00:19:09,700 --> 00:19:11,950
Are you doing fine?

227
00:19:13,230 --> 00:19:14,730
Yes.

228
00:19:42,210 --> 00:19:45,150
What do you think? Do you like it?

229
00:19:45,150 --> 00:19:47,330
I like it.

230
00:19:49,060 --> 00:19:51,980
You were uncomfortable at the hotel.

231
00:19:52,710 --> 00:19:55,080
So you can be comfortable here.

232
00:19:56,520 --> 00:19:59,280
You really are the same Cha Seo Hoo.

233
00:20:08,490 --> 00:20:10,120
Phone call from France

234
00:20:11,610 --> 00:20:13,570
Just a minute.

235
00:20:43,770 --> 00:20:46,180
What is this place?

236
00:20:52,460 --> 00:20:57,430
Where I'll be living now, and... where you'll be.

237
00:20:59,100 --> 00:21:00,730
Do you like it?

238
00:21:05,860 --> 00:21:07,530
Surprise.

239
00:21:09,110 --> 00:21:10,360
What is this?

240
00:21:10,360 --> 00:21:12,110
The key to this place.

241
00:21:18,120 --> 00:21:19,660
Come every day.

242
00:21:24,090 --> 00:21:28,980
Was I just proposed to? This easily?

243
00:22:02,930 --> 00:22:05,600
I have to prepare for the day after tomorrow's function.

244
00:22:05,600 --> 00:22:09,900
Let me receive Team Leader Oh's skill. It's been awhile.

245
00:22:21,240 --> 00:22:25,220
See if it suits your liking, the way I prepared it.

246
00:22:33,270 --> 00:22:36,340
I really can't stop you, Cha Seo Hoo.

247
00:22:46,770 --> 00:22:48,970
Here you go.

248
00:22:48,970 --> 00:22:50,380
Love's Food Car.

249
00:22:52,810 --> 00:22:55,650
Whoa! That's cool!
- You're good!

250
00:22:55,650 --> 00:22:57,880
Eat a lot.

251
00:22:57,880 --> 00:22:59,450
Smile a bit.

252
00:22:59,450 --> 00:23:02,260
How can you understand my broken heart?

253
00:23:02,260 --> 00:23:04,990
I will recommend you for the kindest flight attendant next time, so cheer up.

254
00:23:04,990 --> 00:23:07,020
I don't need any of it.

