00:46:43,430 --> 00:46:45,760
because of Choi Won?

512
00:46:46,920 --> 00:46:48,110
What?

513
00:46:48,110 --> 00:46:50,340
I am asking if it is because of Choi Won?

514
00:46:52,570 --> 00:46:54,910
Why are you bringing that up now?

515
00:46:54,910 --> 00:46:58,040
As always Choi Won who is at the end of our problems.

516
00:46:58,040 --> 00:46:59,720
How is our problem caused by Choi Won?

517
00:46:59,720 --> 00:47:03,770
Why haven't you asked me why I didn't show myself to you when I told you I've returned?

518
00:47:03,770 --> 00:47:07,190
You should have asked me why I just turned back.

519
00:47:07,190 --> 00:47:11,710
And why I didn't come back. Why aren't you asking me that?

520
00:47:11,710 --> 00:47:14,770
What difference does it make if I know that?

521
00:47:14,770 --> 00:47:19,000
I thought if we meet again then our past has to be forgotten.

522
00:47:19,000 --> 00:47:23,300
Because the moment we bring it up, it will hurt us.

523
00:47:24,310 --> 00:47:28,760
That nothing happened before and I have forgotten like that.

524
00:47:28,760 --> 00:47:31,600
I can't forget that Oh Ha Na.

525
00:47:31,600 --> 00:47:34,970
The fact you were crying in Choi Won's arms that day.

526
00:47:35,950 --> 00:47:41,390
And your smiling face in front of that punk despite the pain I caused.

527
00:47:41,390 --> 00:47:43,480
I can never forget it.

528
00:47:44,630 --> 00:47:46,530
Seo Hoo.

529
00:47:49,590 --> 00:47:52,630
When I said I won't make the same mistake twice,

530
00:47:54,410 --> 00:48:00,700
I mean I won't lose you ever again whether it is due to Choi Won or not.

531
00:48:30,060 --> 00:48:37,080
Timing and Subtitles brought to you by The Timeless Lovers @ Viki

532
00:49:11,810 --> 00:49:13,480
Oh Ha Na!

533
00:49:18,520 --> 00:49:20,300
What are you doing there?

534
00:49:20,300 --> 00:49:22,910
What are you doing here?

535
00:49:22,910 --> 00:49:25,100
Running an Errand for Madam Choi.

536
00:49:25,100 --> 00:49:29,240
Uh... Go on in.

537
00:49:29,240 --> 00:49:30,540
Aren't you going in?

538
00:49:30,540 --> 00:49:32,300
I should.

539
00:49:49,420 --> 00:49:52,650
Did something happen, by any chance?

540
00:49:52,650 --> 00:49:55,720
No, nothing.

541
00:49:58,190 --> 00:50:03,010
Our relationship is such that we can read each other's faces.

542
00:50:03,810 --> 00:50:05,710
- Oh Ha Na.
- I know.

543
00:50:05,710 --> 00:50:11,110
I am aware of our relationship that we can just look at the facial expressions and know what's going on. That's why I am going in.

544
00:50:11,110 --> 00:50:13,270
I am asking what is going on?

545
00:50:13,270 --> 00:50:16,190
What is it about? And what is difficult?

546
00:50:16,190 --> 00:50:18,370
I have nothing difficult.

547
00:50:19,990 --> 00:50:21,950
Don't worry about it.

548
00:50:24,550 --> 00:50:28,570
Oh Ha Ha, I told you I'll be your friend.

549
00:50:28,570 --> 00:50:31,890
Didn't I tell you that I'd be on your side?

550
00:50:35,330 --> 00:50:38,870
I know. That's why...

551
00:50:39,710 --> 00:50:42,990
Because you know too much...

552
00:50:42,990 --> 00:50:45,510
Because you know all of it...

553
00:50:45,510 --> 00:50:48,270
I can't say anything to you.

554
00:50:49,830 --> 00:50:55,110
Our relationship now... must be that way.

555
00:50:59,610 --> 00:51:01,470
I'll get going first.

556
00:51:26,930 --> 00:51:30,250
The fact you were crying in Choi Won's arms that day.

557
00:51:31,270 --> 00:51:36,590
And your smiling face in front of that punk despite the pain I caused.

558
00:51:36,590 --> 00:51:38,710
I will never forget it.

559
00:51:53,930 --> 00:51:55,290
There isn't any problem, is there?

560
00:51:55,290 --> 00:51:59,090
Of course not. You can relax.

561
00:52:00,030 --> 00:52:02,170
Team Leader Oh!

562
00:52:02,170 --> 00:52:05,590
She is the President of Cha Seo Hoo's contracting company.

563
00:52:05,590 --> 00:52:08,410
Hello I am Team Leader Oh Ha Na.

564
00:52:08,410 --> 00:52:12,310
I've heard a lot about you. I am Min Ji Soo.

565
00:52:14,770 --> 00:52:19,350
It probably wasn't easy,  but taking Cha Seo Hoo's project to the end...

566
00:52:19,350 --> 00:52:23,590
And I heard you did it alone, is it right?

567
00:52:25,830 --> 00:52:27,850
My Seo Hoo...

568
00:52:28,790 --> 00:52:30,930
Please take good care of him.

569
00:52:38,130 --> 00:52:41,000
Hello, I will give you the briefing.

570
00:52:41,000 --> 00:52:46,000
Aria plane leaving Incheon Airport bound to Tokyo is departing at 9:25 a.m.

571
00:52:46,000 --> 00:52:49,860
The total flight time is about 2 hours and 35 minutes.

572
00:52:49,860 --> 00:52:52,170
We have about 120 reservations.

573
00:52:52,170 --> 00:52:55,760
I can't tell you anything.

574
00:52:55,760 --> 00:53:01,350
Our relationship now...must be that way.

575
00:53:05,690 --> 00:53:11,250
I ask for your full cooperation to make this flight safe and enjoyable.

576
00:53:24,050 --> 00:53:28,440
- It will be the end of our friendship If you come empty handed.
- If you don't come, your number will be deleted.

577
00:53:37,880 --> 00:53:42,600
I heard Cha Seo Hoo had some scandals with his sponsor while living overseas.

578
00:53:42,600 --> 00:53:45,950
Did you see that President Min's force? She won't play around.

579
00:53:45,950 --> 00:53:48,470
Isn't he dating Team Leader Oh?

580
00:53:48,470 --> 00:53:50,170
It seems so.

581
00:54:02,640 --> 00:54:08,220
I heard Cha Seo Hoo had some scandals with his sponsor while living overseas.

582
00:54:19,170 --> 00:54:23,850
The person at this number is not available...
Cha Seo Hoo

583
00:54:39,400 --> 00:54:42,770
Invitation for housewarming party. Time: Next Friday at 6pm. Place: The newlyweds house
It will be the end of our friendship if you come empty handed

584
00:54:53,090 --> 00:54:57,630
The Director says he wants to ensure the benefit performance goes as planned,

585
00:54:57,630 --> 00:55:01,790
so he wants to wrap up the concert poster concept by today.

586
00:55:05,110 --> 00:55:06,820
Uh, okay.

587
00:55:06,820 --> 00:55:11,260
I think that President Min is quite a capable person.

588
00:55:11,270 --> 00:55:14,380
The director has totally changed since her visit yesterday.

589
00:55:14,380 --> 00:55:16,010
Is that right?

590
00:55:16,650 --> 00:55:21,770
But Cha Seo Hoo is not coming by lately. He used to visit frequently.

591
00:55:21,770 --> 00:55:25,880
Assistant Hong? Didn't you say we need to wrap up the concept by today?

592
00:55:25,880 --> 00:55:27,210
Yeah.

593
00:56:01,210 --> 00:56:06,470
(Toilet tissue is a frequent Korean housewarming gift so everything rolls easily in life and life is long.)

594
00:56:13,340 --> 00:56:15,200
Let's go.

595
00:56:22,330 --> 00:56:25,680
How are you guys bring housewarming gifts like they're buy one get one free.

596
00:56:25,680 --> 00:56:28,730
No. We bought them separately.

597
00:56:28,730 --> 00:56:31,400
They brought this for us to get rich. The more the better. Besides you use a lot.

598
00:56:31,400 --> 00:56:32,600
- Thank you. Thank you.
- What is this?

599
00:56:32,600 --> 00:56:35,830
Even the brand is the same. You guys are really funny.

600
00:56:35,830 --> 00:56:37,540
Enough with the teasing.

601
00:56:37,540 --> 00:56:39,670
Guys, Chang Soo prepared this.

602
00:56:40,960 --> 00:56:42,930
Right, you can't cook, Jeong Mi.

603
00:56:42,960 --> 00:56:46,640
No. All I have to do is lift my chopsticks.

604
00:56:46,640 --> 00:56:49,130
My hands don't have a chance to get dried.

605
00:56:49,130 --> 00:56:51,220
Sit, sit.

606
00:56:51,220 --> 00:56:54,160
- You know I don't like salty foods, right?
- This is really great!

607
00:56:54,160 --> 00:56:56,790
It'll be bland. I'm sorry.

608
00:56:59,380 --> 00:57:02,220
-,This looks really delicious.
-,Right.

609
00:57:02,220 --> 00:57:04,250
Eat a lot.

610
00:57:06,510 --> 00:57:08,920
The second round is an Italian style—

611
00:57:08,920 --> 00:57:10,990
Pizza!

612
00:57:10,990 --> 00:57:13,500
Eat again? Are you raising us like animals?

613
00:57:13,500 --> 00:57:15,620
My stomach is about to burst and kill me.

614
00:57:15,620 --> 00:57:20,270
I heard you must eat a lot at a housewarming party, so we prepared plenty.

615
00:57:20,300 --> 00:57:22,670
Right, right. Let's eat, let's eat.

616
00:57:22,670 --> 00:57:25,630
I've been trying to lose weight these days.

617
00:57:25,630 --> 00:57:29,300
I heard the weight, at this age, is not easy to lose...

618
00:57:29,300 --> 00:57:35,340
Now that we are having a housewarming party, I remember Won's girlfriend's housewarming party before.

619
00:57:35,340 --> 00:57:38,540
- When?
- Do you remember In Ni?

620
00:57:39,260 --> 00:57:42,460
Ah! In Ni ... When I was in college.

621
00:57:42,460 --> 00:57:48,090
After In Ni, you haven't had a serious relationship, Choi Won.

622
00:57:48,110 --> 00:57:51,800
I remember her now! Ha Na really hated her.

623
00:57:51,800 --> 00:57:54,590
- When did I hate her?
- You hated her.

624
00:57:54,590 --> 00:57:56,660
I don't remember!

625
00:57:56,660 --> 00:58:00,370
- Won! Do you want me show you those graduation pictures I told you about?
- Yes!

626
00:58:00,370 --> 00:58:06,110
- Graduation pictures?
- I saved this because it was interesting.

627
00:58:07,780 --> 00:58:09,740
Ah, I do remember.

628
00:58:09,740 --> 00:58:12,800
I am probably the only one who took a leave from the military service to take graduation pictures.

629
00:58:12,800 --> 00:58:17,320
What about me giving up my training in Paris and almost getting fired?

630
00:58:17,320 --> 00:58:21,710
But you didn't get fired and you went to Paris for training.

631
00:58:21,750 --> 00:58:25,720
I did go to Paris... Then...

632
00:58:25,720 --> 00:58:28,710
You met Cha Seo Hoo there, didn't you?

633
00:58:29,800 --> 00:58:31,710
You did!

634
00:58:31,710 --> 00:58:35,520
Then you met Cha Seo Hoo because of Won?

635
00:58:35,540 --> 00:58:38,700
Wow! How can this happen? This is so interesting.

636
00:58:38,700 --> 00:58:42,220
If you guys are lovers then your destiny is totally off.

637
00:58:42,220 --> 00:58:44,340
It seems so.

638
00:58:44,340 --> 00:58:47,340
Aside from the graduation photo issue,

639
00:58:47,340 --> 00:58:51,240
is there another memory of a special one-plus-one case? This is fun.

640
00:58:51,240 --> 00:58:54,260
We are the guests of honor today.

641
00:58:54,270 --> 00:58:55,920
Let's eat!

642
00:58:55,920 --> 00:58:59,190
- Jeong Mi, why did you marry him?
- Because he's good looking.

643
00:58:59,260 --> 00:59:01,200
My man's face is important.

644
00:59:01,200 --> 00:59:04,040
Are you getting nauseous?

645
00:59:04,040 --> 00:59:05,450
Let's eat!

646
00:59:24,350 --> 00:59:30,170
So they've dated a long time before getting married and  are still like friends.

647
00:59:30,200 --> 00:59:35,840
They looked good. It felt like they were living as friends and not as newlyweds.

648
00:59:37,180 --> 00:59:42,880
Hearing about your forgotten past love was fun too.

649
00:59:42,960 --> 00:59:47,920
Oh Ha Na's love story isn't one to be belittled either.

650
00:59:49,430 --> 00:59:55,340
How did we live through those times...

651
00:59:58,920 --> 01:00:01,020
Oh Ha Na!

652
01:00:02,590 --> 01:00:04,050
Hm?

653
01:00:05,210 --> 01:00:08,220
Don't you think our relationship is something great?

654
01:00:09,550 --> 01:00:15,380
What don't we know about each other in this long time span?

655
01:00:18,210 --> 01:00:21,000
We know it all.

656
01:00:21,000 --> 01:00:28,340
Because we saw them together, we remember all those times.

657
01:00:30,070 --> 01:00:34,240
So that's what I am saying, Oh Ha Na.

658
01:00:34,240 --> 01:00:39,880
Saying things like, "I can't tell you. Our relationship must be that way..."

659
01:00:39,880 --> 01:00:43,630
Try saying that one more time...

660
01:00:51,530 --> 01:00:54,880
Let's not get to where we can't even be friends.

661
01:00:57,700 --> 01:01:01,140
Let's go back...

662
01:01:01,220 --> 01:01:04,710
to the place where we were joyous and had fun.

663
01:01:05,590 --> 01:01:11,770
♬ I couldn't say no ♬

