♬ is a long and endless journey ♬

667
01:01:31,000 --> 01:01:37,460
♬ I'm heading toward you ♬

668
01:01:37,470 --> 01:01:43,840
♬ We will always be the same ♬

669
01:01:43,930 --> 01:01:50,230
♬ Turn around and look at me ♬

670
01:01:50,280 --> 01:01:56,780
♬ I will take care of you forever ♬

671
01:01:56,830 --> 01:02:02,130
♬ I'm heading toward you ♬

672
01:02:03,040 --> 01:02:04,870
I have someone I want to introduce to you.

673
01:02:04,870 --> 01:02:06,550
We meet here, huh?

674
01:02:06,550 --> 01:02:08,320
I'm sorry, Unni.

675
01:02:08,320 --> 01:02:10,000
Why? Because of Won?

676
01:02:10,000 --> 01:02:15,200
And I thought that becoming close to you again would be too selfish of me.

677
01:02:15,200 --> 01:02:20,570
The long time that we have spent together doesn't have to become a dating relationship or love.

678
01:02:20,570 --> 01:02:21,920
Oh Ha Na!

679
01:02:23,090 --> 01:02:28,270
Whether it's as a friend or whatever, I can't tolerate your being close to Oh Ha Na.

680
01:02:28,270 --> 01:02:31,590
Your sudden appearance is not welcome.

681
01:02:31,590 --> 01:02:34,860
If I were to get rid of Oh Ha Na from Cha Seo Hoo's side,

682
01:02:34,860 --> 01:02:38,930
are you going to keep your agreement with me?

683
01:02:38,990 --> 01:02:44,220
♬ I'm heading toward you ♬
